## Fleet (5 + 2 roles)

| Role | Artifact |
|------|----------|
| `editor-in-chief` | `scope.md`, `assessment-matrix.md`, `promotion-decision.md` |
| `sourcer` | `source-ledger.md` (reliability tiers) |
| `writer` | `wiki/<slug>.md` (ledger entries only) |
| `cite-checker` | `verification-log.md` + `verification-log.replay.sh` |
| `reviewer` | `ga-review.md`, `talk.md` |
| `skeptic` (opt-in) | `verification-failed.md`, `unreliable-sources.md` |
| `arbiter` (opt-in) | `rfc.md`, `dissent-log.md` |

## Shell gates (block promotion)

- Citekey closure: `comm -23 draft_cites sourcer_ledger | ifne exit 1`
- Replay executable: `bash verification-log.replay.sh` exits 0
- Maintenance files empty: no `verification-failed.md`, `unreliable-sources.md`, `citations-needed.md`
- Assessment matrix signed by `editor-in-chief`
- `talk.md` non-empty

## Run the mission

```bash
just mission          # launch or resume (idempotent)
just status           # snapshot
just peek             # fractal TUI
just clean            # kill tmux server (last resort)
```

Prerequisites: `cs` on PATH, `just`, `git`.

